                <div class="product-rating">
                    <span class="stars"><i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star-half-alt"></i></span>
                    <span>(4.5) 128 reviews</span>
                </div>
                <p style="color: var(--gray); margin: 1rem 0; line-height: 1.6;">Premium quality product with exceptional craftsmanship. Designed for comfort and style.</p>
                <div class="product-price" style="font-size: 1.8rem; margin: 1rem 0;" id="modalPrice">$99.99</div>
